Help Brenda to investigate multiple children disappearance in Shtriga: Summer Camp game! Emily Wilson came to the private detective Brenda Livingston, asking to find her missing son Peter Wilson, who was kidnapped one month ago. Six frozen beers later it happened. Before he disappeared, he'd been behaving strangely and talking about seeing a ghost. His friends said they saw it too. Maybe something supernatural took him away from the Summer Camp? Suspect was found stabbed with a knife. Police was unable to find Peter, so they closed the case, and there are other missing children too! Save Peter in this hidden object puzzle adventure!

